headline: Redburn Atlantic downgrades rating of Starbucks to "Sell"
summary: Investing.com - Analysts at Redburn Atlantic have lowered their rating of Starbucks (NASDAQ:SBUX) to "Sell," arguing that the consensus outlook for the coffee chain does not "adequately reflect" the costs associated with the company's sweeping turnaround plans.
